{"tid":1823882,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"想立法2020普選就唔選得功能組別, 想港獨就只可以揭竿起義 唔可以選議會做任何公職公務員??","createTime":"2020-01-14T04:42:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-14T04:58:52.000Z","uid":130406,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"97d687f47e8f1563e9099004c8addf6d695fab1e","tid":1823882,"uid":130406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T04:42:45.000Z","msg":"如果想立法2020普選就唔選得功能組別, <br />\n咁想港獨就一定只可以揭竿起義 <br />\n唔可以選議會做任何公職公務員??<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">而家問題並非想選邊個 入到去會做到咩<br />\n而係唔想保皇黨選到 阻止佢做到咩</span></strong></strong></span><br />\n我就係寧願射落海選個0分陳梓維都唔撚益民建聯律師呀<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">記住香港所謂議會從來非民主制度<br />\n只係斯騙外國人嚟做生意嘅公仔箱騙局</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n唔通支持港獨又選等如認同港共制度<br />\n揾議員幫手就等如承認議會公正？"},{"pid":"c7605d09674432a003d4ef008f4140c30529995f","tid":1823882,"uid":130406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T04:44:13.000Z","msg":"香"},{"pid":"852b67d97143cd9b9aa858da46abdc395cf9e11b","tid":1823882,"uid":130406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T04:44:47.000Z","msg":"港"},{"pid":"a9526139d14b7519a1a47f28bf77283c6120e670","tid":1823882,"uid":130406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T04:45:13.000Z","msg":"獨"},{"pid":"5cae0d379cf83ea005e1d394be9928c7126ab8bc","tid":1823882,"uid":130406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T04:45:28.000Z","msg":"立"},{"pid":"8d2b8d9368ab085eeaf9b29d3712689999d1e5f3","tid":1823882,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T04:46:48.000Z","msg":"沒有普選 唯有獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"593a11c855113c4ec2fe326265694842b8edf1ac","tid":1823882,"uid":130406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T04:52:40.000Z","msg":"香"},{"pid":"0f46dd7771356ea4bd6d90